column17: SELECT t.caseno, t.amount, ac.Bailtype,Year(ac.DateReceived) as BailYear, max(s.CaseStatus) as BailStatus,max(s.CaseStatus)MAXID, max(h.comment) as Comment
FROM dbo.History GROUP BY CaseNo, Comment ) h
on h.caseno = hh.caseno and h.HistID = hh.HistoryId
inner join ( select max(StatusId)MAXST, CaseNo, CaseStatus from dbo.Status group by
on s.caseno = ss.caseno and s.MAXST = ss.StatusId
where ac.casetype ='2'  and ac.Bailtype = '2' and Year(ac.DateReceived) < '2015'
group by t.caseno, t.amount, ac.Bailtype, Year(ac.DateReceived)
